JSWCTimer args;state;f1
⍝ Rotate the colours


:Select ⊃args
:Case 'F1.TM' ⍝ Timer
   'F1.T1' ∆WS 'FCol' (1⌽'F1.T1' ∆WG 'FCol')
⍝   ⎕←'FireOnce: ',⍕f1←'F1.TM' ∆WG 'FireOnce'
⍝   'F1.F1' ∆WS 'State' (f1=1)
:Case 'F1.AC' ⍝ Active
   state←'F1.AC' ∆WG 'State'
   'F1.TM' ∆WS 'Active' state
:Case 'F1.F1' ⍝ Fire once
   'F1.TM' ∆WS 'FireOnce' ('F1.F1' ∆WG 'State')
:EndSelect
